snippet.title: Cukies World Metaverse Gameplay Teaser (05-12-2021)
snippet.description:
Cukies World coming soon: Q1 2022

Mint yours and get ready: https://Cukies.World

Less than 4,000 Cukies left! Holding a Cuki allows you to play the game and get rewards. It also gives you access to UKI token private sale. The more Cukies you have, the higher your allocation for the private sale will be!

Learn more in our telegram group:
https://t.me/cukiesworld
